[package]
name = "auth-common"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["Acrimon <joel.wejdenstal@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
rand = "0.8"

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.4.1"
default-features = false
features = ["serde", "v4"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.115"
default-features = false
features = ["derive"]

[package]
name = "authc"
version = "1.0.0"
authors = ["Acrimon <joel.wejdenstal@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
http = "1.1"
hyper-util = "0.1"
http-body-util = "0.1"
bytes = "1"
serde_json = "1.0"
hex = "0.4.3"
fxhash = "0.2.1"

[dependencies.hyper]
version = "1"
default-features = false
features = ["client", "http1"]

[dependencies.hyper-rustls]
version = "0.27"
default-features = false
features = ["http1", "ring", "native-tokio"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.115"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.8"
default-features = false
features = ["serde", "v4"]

[dependencies.auth-common]
path = "../common"

[dependencies.rust-argon2]
version = "2.1.0"
default-features = false

[package]
name = "conrod_core"
version = "0.63.0"
authors = ["Mitchell Nordine <mitchell.nordine@gmail.com>", "Sven Nilsen <bvssvni@gmail.com>"]
keywords = ["ui", "widgets", "gui", "interface", "graphics"]
description = "An easy-to-use, 100% Rust, extensible 2D GUI library."
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "../README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod.git"
homepage = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod"
documentation = "http://docs.piston.rs/conrod/conrod/"
categories = ["gui"]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true

[features]
stdweb = ["instant/stdweb"]
wasm-bindgen = ["instant/wasm-bindgen"]

[dependencies]
daggy = "0.5"
fnv = "1.0"
num = "0.2"
pistoncore-input = "0.24"
instant = "0.1"
copypasta = "0.8"

[dependencies.conrod_derive]
path = "../conrod_derive"
version = "0.63"

[dependencies.rusttype]
version = "0.7"
features = ["gpu_cache"]

[package]
name = "conrod_derive"
version = "0.63.0"
authors = ["mitchmindtree <mitchell.nordine@gmail.com>"]
description = "A crate providing procedural macros for the conrod library"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
keywords = ["conrod", "gui", "derive", "procedural", "macro"]
repository = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod.git"
homepage = "https://github.com/pistondevelopers/conrod"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "0.4.2"
quote = "0.6"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "0.15"
features = ["extra-traits", "full"]

[package]
name = "iced_core"
version = "0.4.0"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"
description = "The essential concepts of Iced"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/iced"

[dependencies.palette]
version = "0.5.0"
optional = true

[package]
name = "iced_futures"
version = "0.3.0"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"
description = "Commands, subscriptions, and runtimes for Iced"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/iced"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/iced_futures"
keywords = ["gui", "ui", "graphics", "interface", "futures"]
categories = ["gui"]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
rustdoc-args = ["--cfg", "docsrs"]
all-features = true

[features]
thread-pool = ["futures/thread-pool"]

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"

[dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.tokio_old]
package = "tokio"
version = "0.2"
optional = true
features = ["rt-core", "rt-threaded", "time", "stream"]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.tokio]
package = "tokio"
version = "1.0"
optional = true
features = ["rt", "rt-multi-thread", "time"]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.async-std]
version = "1.0"
optional = true
features = ["unstable"]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.smol]
version = "1.2"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4"

[package]
name = "iced_native"
version = "0.4.0"
authors = ["Héctor Ramón Jiménez <hector0193@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"
description = "A renderer-agnostic library for native GUIs"
license = "MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/hecrj/iced"

[features]
debug = []

[dependencies]
twox-hash = "1.5"
unicode-segmentation = "1.6"
num-traits = "0.2"

[dependencies.iced_core]
version = "0.4"
path = "../core"

[dependencies.iced_futures]
version = "0.3"
path = "../futures"
features = ["thread-pool"]

[package]
name = "portpicker"
description = "Pick a free unused port"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["Hannes Karppila <hannes.karppila@gmail.com>"]
edition = "2018"
repository = "https://github.com/Dentosal/portpicker-rs"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["port", "network"]
categories = ["network-programming"]
license = "Unlicense"

[dependencies]
rand = "0.8"

[package]
name = "specs"
version = "0.20.0"
description = "Specs is an Entity-Component-System library written in Rust.\n"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/specs/"
repository = "https://github.com/amethyst/specs"
homepage = "https://amethyst.github.io/specs"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["gamedev", "ecs", "entity", "component"]
categories = ["concurrency", "game-engines"]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
authors = ["slide-rs hackers"]
include = ["/src", "/examples", "/benches", "/README.md", "/LICENSE-MIT", "/LICENSE-APACHE"]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70.0"
autobenches = false

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = ["parallel", "serde", "shred-derive", "specs-derive", "uuid_entity", "storage-event-control"]

[dependencies]
ahash = "0.8.6"
crossbeam-queue = "0.3"
log = "0.4.8"
shrev = "1.1.1"
tuple_utils = "0.4.0"
nougat = "0.2.3"

[dependencies.hibitset]
version = "0.6.4"
default-features = false

[dependencies.shred]
version = "0.16.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.rayon]
version = "1.5.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.104"
optional = true
features = ["serde_derive"]

[dependencies.specs-derive]
version = "0.4.1"
path = "specs-derive"
optional = true

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.0"
optional = true
features = ["v4", "serde"]

[features]
default = ["parallel"]
parallel = ["dep:rayon", "shred/parallel", "hibitset/parallel"]
uuid_entity = ["dep:uuid", "serde"]
stdweb = ["dep:uuid", "uuid?/js"]
storage-event-control = []
derive = ["shred-derive", "specs-derive"]
nightly = ["shred/nightly"]
shred-derive = ["shred/shred-derive"]

[dev-dependencies]
nalgebra = "0.32"
criterion = "0.3.1"
ron = "0.8.1"
rand = "0.8"
serde_json = "1.0.48"

[dev-dependencies.shred]
version = "0.16.0"
default-features = false
features = ["shred-derive"]

[dev-dependencies.specs-derive]
path = "specs-derive"
version = "0.4.1"

[[example]]
name = "async"

[[example]]
name = "basic"

[[example]]
name = "bitset"

[[example]]
name = "cluster_bomb"

[[example]]
name = "full"

[[example]]
name = "lend_join"
test = true

[[example]]
name = "ordered_track"

[[example]]
name = "saveload"
required-features = ["serde"]

[[example]]
name = "slices"

[[example]]
name = "track"

[[bench]]
name = "benches_main"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "parallel"

[[bench]]
name = "world"
harness = false

[[bench]]
name = "big_or_small"

[workspace]
members = ["specs-derive"]

[package]
name = "specs-derive"
version = "0.4.1"
authors = ["Eyal Kalderon <ebkalderon@gmail.com>"]
description = "Custom derive macro for Specs components"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/specs-derive"
repository = "https://github.com/slide-rs/specs/tree/master/specs-derive"
keywords = ["gamedev", "parallel", "specs", "ecs", "derive"]
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0.8"
syn = "1.0.14"
quote = "1.0.2"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://gitlab.com/veloren/auth"]
git = "https://gitlab.com/veloren/auth"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "ae0e16783a9f9041951296885f082308e155db79"

[source."https://gitlab.com/veloren/conrod"]
git = "https://gitlab.com/veloren/conrod"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "copypasta_0.7"

[source."https://github.com/imberflur/iced"]
git = "https://github.com/imberflur/iced"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
tag = "veloren-winit-0.28"

[source."https://github.com/xmac94x/portpicker-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/xmac94x/portpicker-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "df6b37872f3586ac3b21d08b56c8ec7cd92fb172"

[source."https://github.com/amethyst/specs"]
git = "https://github.com/amethyst/specs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "4e2da1df29ee840baa9b936593c45592b7c9ae27"
